TheMysteryOfEdwinDrood1 = TheMysteryOfEdwinDrood %>%
  
  str_replace_all("\"","") %>% 
  str_replace_all("[[:punct:]]","") %>% 
  str_split(pattern = "\\s") %>% 
  unlist() %>% 
  str_to_lower() %>% 
  removeWords(., stopwords('en')) %>% 
  str_trim() %>% 
  table() %>% 
  as.data.frame(stringsAsFactors = F)

TheMysteryOfEdwinDrood1 %>% arrange(-Freq) -> TheMysteryOfEdwinDrood1
r = TheMysteryOfEdwinDrood1[3:22 ,]
ggplot(r , aes(x = reorder(. , -Freq) , y = Freq)) + geom_col()

  wstone = ThePickwickPapers %>% 
    str_replace_all("\"","") %>% 
    str_replace_all("[[:punct:]]","") %>% 
    str_split(pattern = "\\s") %>% 
    unlist() %>% 
    table() %>% 
    as.data.frame(stringsAsFactors = F)
  colnames(wstone) = c("word","count")
  
  
  wstone = wstone %>% 
    filter(!str_to_lower(word) %in% stopwords('en')) %>% 
    filter(str_length(word)>1) %>% 
    filter(!str_detect(word,"\\d")) %>% 
    arrange(desc(count)) %>% 
    mutate(proper = !word %in% str_to_lower(word)) 
 
  
  
ggplot(data = wstone[1:5,], aes(reorder(word, -count), y = count)) + geom_bar(stat = 'identity',na.rm = TRUE)
